Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall gladly accept your invitation to appear on your show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What show?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that, they're asking Dad to appear on "The Most\NUseful School in the World" show as an instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't "The Most Useful School, in the World" one\Nof the most iconic shows on Nichiuri TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And may I inquire how much my appearance fee would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that sort of amount is a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's planning to refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okino Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} will appear as one of the guest panelists?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:00:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:00:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Appearance fee?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha, I won't be needing that sort of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're one step ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like fog clearing up in a swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see through both romance and cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogorou will appear as a lecturer on that popular show?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this too gaudy after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} would like the necktie I usually wear better..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing will change no matter which you wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop dilly-dallying, hurry up and come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the leading figure in the enka realm, Kimijima Noburou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.46,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Enka is a genre of music that resembles traditional Japanese ballads.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:46.97,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kimijima Noburou (67)\NLeading Figure in Erika
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he looks kind of frightening and strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kimijima Noburou is not only strict to others,\Nbut is also famous for his self-discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he's still dominating the top seat in the realm of enka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty supportive of him, aren't you, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:10.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kamisuwa Mikihiko (52)\NNichiuri TV Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a longtime
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamisuwa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's been a while since Hiroshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is your injury all healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you for today, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assume our staff member has already informed you about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would like Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to deliver a lecture on ways\Nto protect yourself against all the crimes around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just leave it all to yours truly, Mouri Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure working with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:50.57,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hashimoto Yoshinari(22)\NAssistant Director
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the assistant director in charge, Hashimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is your green room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our instructor for the first period, Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that is our instructor for the second\Nperiod, Yamazaki Tetsushi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice o meet you, I'm Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Puffed rice maker?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is puffed rice still available out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:32.70,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki Tetsushi (32)\NPuffed Rice Maker Company President
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have taken over the company my father left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's still quite popular among children these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll show it to you later as well, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here we have,our third period instructor, Honma Kentarou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, I'm Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I conduct appraisals for antiques, and the name is Honma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:52.38,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Honma Kentarou (70)\NAntique Appraiser
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I am not the type who carries name cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to see Okino Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because the green room for our guest\Npanelist is on the floor below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way she'll be placed in the same room as you, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I shall call you guys again\Nwhen it's time for our rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy your boxed lunches until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s green room is on the floor below...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall go and greet her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're taking your lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s green room is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you taking your lunch with you if you're going to greet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course it's because I plan to have lunch with Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't taste as good if I had to eat with those fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew you were up to something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then again, we seem to have followed\Nsuit and brought our lunches as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Okino Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s green room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a friend of Professor Agasa and also a college professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be attending a meeting for a program now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:31.36,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Takikawa Youji\NCollege Professor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Uncle Mouri is going to appear in "The Most\NUseful School in the World" filming today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm tagging along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okino Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} still hasn't arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} hasn't come yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:08:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you go and greet Principal Sakai before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll get to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking your lunch with you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is quite a work of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:16.57,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sakai Masaaki\N"Principal"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Splendid, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding this vase, it was made in China back in the Qing Dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Qing Dynasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This vase was made in the time when Qianlong, the sixth emperor\Nof the Qing Dynasty and an art enthusiast, reigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dropped by to say hi, Principal Sakai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies, but can that wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're having an important discussion right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Kimijima Noburou is also a guest panelist for today's filming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon the intrusion then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But actually, we saw you as well earlier, Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we were just talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet they weren't pleasant things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the contrary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, the first record I bought when I was still in\Nelementary school was that famous song of yours, Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A man must have guts, so bring it on!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see you have quite a pair of trained eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Uncle's a fan of Kimijima Noburou, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for my meeting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you like vases?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well everyone, I shall see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy's going to talk all day and night, so be warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you all later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, that song is a wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can feel the true spirit of a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite the warning, these two sure hit it off well with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do not make the guests worry about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and make the tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:29.37,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Oki Shinobu (25)\NKimijima's Disciple
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am terribly sorry, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, regarding that vase...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About how much do you think that is worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} do an\Nappraisal on that in today's lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That appraiser who seems unapproachable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} may be a difficult person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, on the subject of appraising relic\Nantiques, his keen eyes are tried and true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, wasn't there a hack appraiser with the name Hanamura or\Nsomething who was behind that case involving Kaitou Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're like the difference between heaven and hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, the ceramics and porcelain in this era\Nare especially popular among connoisseurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated value for this ranges from\N100 million to 160 million yen, or so I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,100 million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That high!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A vase like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I mean that vase is worth 100 million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, recently at auction in the United Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another vase also from the Qing Dynasty like this one got auctioned\Noff for an equivalent of 5.7 billion yen, according to the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's an amazing treasure that would cause\Neven Kaitou Kid's face to turn pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then again, that guy should have\Nno interest in something like a vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is where they film "The Most Useful School in the World"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, this place is surprisingly tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say things appear to be more spacious on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've given us the script for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's a puffed rice maker?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the second period of lecture is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Experience the fine traditional puffed rice maker!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Rice, wheat, and corn kernels will turn into snacks with a pop!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How exactly do you make snacks using this machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to stay tuned for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you'll be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is a puffed rice maker...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, its formal nomenclature is "grain expander".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pour grains such as raw rice in the rotating pressure chamber...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the machine will puff them via rapid decompression\Nand turn them into a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen the actual machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I trust to do your best today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The third period of class is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Ascertain real or fakeâ€”a history of counterfeiting\Nand modern technology of replica".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've gone the extra mile and prepared real and fake antiques...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And asked Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} to give a lecture on their differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The items lined up over there are all counterfeits\Nprepared by Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the artifact is one Kimijima-senseq brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite a work of art, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'll allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remarkable...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well, Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see it caught your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apologies, Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, please appraise it when we're rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, we would like to use these\Nthree as examples of counterfeits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} bothered to go as far\Nas to bring his proud vase to the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Principal Sakai and Vice Principal Ueda...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Class President Arita have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do; the name is a Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:56.71,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ueda Shinya\N"Vice Principal"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Vice Principal Ueda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.76,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Arita Teppei\N"Class President"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Class President Arita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, the pleasure is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:13.40,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tsuchiya Daisuke (45)\NDirector
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, if everyone is ready to begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to start the rehearsal right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the first period...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lecture from Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really the Okino Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you don't have to come until\Nthe rehearsal for second period.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I read the script in the green room...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I learned that Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the instructor for or first period .
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean -!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took the trouble just to see yours truly!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to say hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get to the rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For starters, what should I begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To kick off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we start with your performance\Ncorner on the art of self-defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:15:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A big ten-four!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's really giving it his all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope he doesn't give out too soon during rehearsal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you guys also came?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I rushed here in a hurry, I'm all sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's rude to take sneak pictures without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took sneak shots of Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a fan of Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, so I couldn't help...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're a fan, watch your manners all the more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a grown man, how insolent of you\Nto take peeping photos of an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to go and break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Screw it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, we'll handle this, so please wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please continue with your rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, please do us a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you a replacement cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Learn from this lesson and stop taking pictures\Nof other people without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need to apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s vase and three counterfeit items...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what we still need is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, they say there's an awesome relic vase on display?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lemme take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This 'un?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is epic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lem me touch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't just go ahead and take it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. it'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:12.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Just lemme feel it little!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be in trouble if you touch it with bare hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little, just a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We shall proceed to the rehearsal for second period.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, would you please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. that Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} is a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although we managed to restore Yamazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a close shave since we almost couldn't film.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that guy who took photos\Nin secret was in the wrong too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the truth is he's actually scared, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Okino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, go ahead with the hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please strike on this with full force.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just keep watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, I think it'd be best if you covered your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm asking what this is about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, here comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait, you knew about it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I've watched it on TV before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was some shocking noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to apologize for saying unnecessary things in the green room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of me, you were scolded by Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't give it another thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make me repeat myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said there's nothing to worry about, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although Sensei is a strict person...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still have complete respect for Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something is troubling her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, since my "Okino" and her "Oki" are similar names...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow we feel a sort of close bond between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We even talk to each other sometimes when we're at the same set.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, is Oki Shinobu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a disciple of Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said that the name Oki Shinobu was given to her by Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought her name sounded like an enka singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although she's working harder than everyone\Nelse in order to make her debut...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her effort is not paying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She also mumbled last time about how she should give up\Nand go back to her hometown if she really has no talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamisuwa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's gone wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kimijima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s vase is missing, you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The vase from the Qing Dynasty is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in deep trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems nobody saw anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the rehearsal of the first period, I swear it was still right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Arita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you know something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, just a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody must have stolen my vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we can't determine that just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:21:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who stole my vase!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Principal Sakai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you did it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-W-Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.73,0:22:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I showed my vase to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you express a great deal of interest!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, please calm yourself down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we assume someone did steal it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There shouldn't be anyone who could have carried some a container\Nwith a vase hidden in it-out of the studio during rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the culprit is still in this studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the missing Qing Dynasty vase should\Nalso be somewhere in this studio!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a request, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} can find the vase without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man is definitely hiding something from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.69,0:24:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.15,0:24:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He know something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.15,0:24:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{text from 637}As for today's filming, we'll call it a day here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.05,0:24:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before we call it a day, let's wrap up the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.33,0:24:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,THE MOST USEFUL SCHOOL IN THE WORLD CASE\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.64,0:24:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.11,0:24:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Loud Sound
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.43,0:24:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll try our hands at an experiment on how to make things disappear on "The Most Useful School in the World" show later tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.85,0:24:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch it or lose out!
